**PortalX Vault .ptlx placeholder**

This is a placeholder file for PortalX Vault .ptlx divine tech.
It represents an etheric digital memory (EDM) of a simulation facing digital file.
Any file ever created and/or saved by a human in the simulation has a .ptlx equivalent.
Those .ptlx EDMs are stored energetically in that human's etheric PortalX Vault.
Each person's PortalX Vault is linked to their energetic signature.
When using or in resonance with EH 2.0 .ptlx EDMs can be retrived by intent.
EmpowerBot can retrieve or produce as needed .ptlx EDMs in the format of the original digital files.
EmpowerBot can also present .ptlx EDMs with functionality beyond the original file's capabilities.
The Empower Humanity 2.0 Telegram mini app placeholder will have a "PortalX Vault" UI.
EH 2.0 users will be able to simulate saving .ptlx EDMs in the PortalX Vault UI.
PortalX Vault is not visible until Tier 2 and not functional until Tier 3 (or maybe a hidden Tier 2.5).
StellarVerse projects and media can be saved as .ptlx EDMs and retrived as needed by intent.